==Description==

The '''Draft snap widget''' is an alternative for the Draft snap toolbar. The widget is only available in the [[Image:Workbench_Draft.svg|24px]] [[Draft_Workbench|Draft Workbench]]. It is an [[#Preferences|optional]] GUI element that is located in the [[Status_bar|Status bar]].

[[Image:Draft_snap_widget_button.png]]
{{Caption|The Draft snap widget}}

==Usage==

See [[Draft_Snap|Draft Snap]].

[[Image:Draft_snap_widget_menu.png]]
{{Caption|The menu of the widget}}

==Preferences==

See also: [[Preferences_Editor|Preferences Editor]] and [[Draft_Preferences|Draft Preferences]].

* The Draft snap widget is optional: {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences... → Draft → Interface → Show the Snap widget in the Draft Workbench}}.


